"Change Set:		8695Kernel-ar.360Kernel-ar.360:Fix small typo in obsoletion - removeTraitUser: should be sent to the elements of the composition.Kernel-ar.359:Final cleanup touches: Avoid unused protocol, remove reclassification."!!ClassDescription methodsFor: 'initialize-release' stamp: 'ar 12/31/2009 15:39'!obsolete	"Make the receiver obsolete."	self hasTraitComposition ifTrue: [		self traitComposition do: [:each |			each removeTraitUser: self]].	superclass removeSubclass: self.	self organization: nil.	super obsolete.! !ClassDescription class removeSelector: #initialize!ClassDescription initialize!